<plot>Charlie Hankinson, the ten-year-old expert on almost everything, is an expert on football in this entry in Paramount's Pacemaker series (production number K11-6). Charlie picks his all-time All-American football team, which includes Glenn Davis and Felix 'Doc' Blanchard from the U.S. Military Academy; University of Michigan's Tom Harmon and the University of Illinois' "The Galloping Ghost." Harold 'Red' Grange. His selection as coach of this mythical team is Herman Hickman from Yale University.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?423301</url></doc>
